@startuml Web Interface Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Mobile Browser" as Browser
participant "Pi Web Server\n(Go HTTP)" as PiServer
participant "GPU Transcription\nService\n(via SSH tunnel)" as GPUService
participant "Pi HID Driver\n(/dev/hidg0)" as HID

== Authentication ==
User -> Browser: Access Pi URL
Browser -> PiServer: GET /
PiServer -> Browser: Serve index.html
User -> Browser: Enter API key
Browser -> Browser: Store key in localStorage

== Recording & Transcription ==
User -> Browser: Press "Start Recording"
Browser -> Browser: MediaRecorder starts
note right: Recording happens\nlocally in browser
User -> Browser: Press "Stop Recording"
Browser -> Browser: MediaRecorder stops
Browser -> Browser: Convert to WAV blob

Browser -> PiServer: POST /transcribe\n(X-API-Key header + audio WAV)
PiServer -> PiServer: Validate API key
alt Invalid API Key
    PiServer -> Browser: 401 Unauthorized
    Browser -> User: Show error status
else Valid API Key
    Browser -> User: Show "processing" status

    PiServer -> GPUService: POST /transcribe\n(forward audio WAV)
    GPUService -> GPUService: Whisper inference
    GPUService -> PiServer: Return transcribed text

    PiServer -> HID: Type text via type-ascii.py
    HID -> User: Text appears on connected device

    PiServer -> Browser: 200 OK
    Browser -> User: Show "success" status
end

@enduml
